ActTransportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of FAYE HELEN SMITH of Gloucester, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Transportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years; and designation of FAYE HELEN SMITH as Chairperson of the Transportation Appeal Tribunal of Canada, effective May 30, 2005.
